{"tid":736271,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 同支那公司合資出 x86 CPU，被稱為「EPYC合法山寨版」！","createTime":"2018-07-10T06:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T09:38:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0375f5649eff8a956fdd28df980a1e85d6c1284b","tid":736271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">AMD EPYC「合法山寨版」？！　中國海光開始生產 X86 架構 CPU<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/07/09/amd-epyc合法山寨版-中國海光開始生產x86架構cpu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2Famd-epyc%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E7%89%88-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%89%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2x86%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8Bcpu%2F&d=G3HZ6pmG21M7rxM7%2BVX0BXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8764a803\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/07/09/amd-epyc合法山寨版-中國海光開始生產x86架構cpu/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/180709-amd-hygon-x86-cpu-dhyana-word-770x439_c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F180709-amd-hygon-x86-cpu-dhyana-word-770x439_c.png&h=319c8db4&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"14962c444484a0e8979b9c2d572715e882c1f50e","tid":736271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"x86 CPU 架構授權，在數十年來都只有 Intel 、 AMD 和 VIA 三大科技巨頭獨攬，因此用於個人電腦、伺服器等高端設備的 CPU 品牌，來來去去都只聽到 Intel 或 AMD （ VIA 則較為力有不逮），然後就再沒有其他品牌能獲權出產 x86 CPU ，形成寡頭壟斷市場。不過「厲害了，我的國」，最近有消息指大陸的晶片製造商海光（ Hygon ）現正開始生產 Dhyana （禪定）系列 x86 CPU ，主要針對伺服器市場，並基於 AMD Zen 微架構開發，但絕非偷取 AMD 的知識產權，或者是抄襲概念的山寨（因此標題用了引號），而是中國合法設計的國產 CPU 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/17570-epyc-logo-chip-straight-view-1260x709.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F17570-epyc-logo-chip-straight-view-1260x709.png&h=4240deb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Dhyana CPU 是 AMD EPYC 的合法山寨版？！</span></div>"},{"pid":"81ff00748f70c058f83285b1f1a6ba7a536a7fe2","tid":736271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那制海光禪定 CPU</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n基於 AMD Zen 架構開發，那代表 Hygon Dhyana CPU 會跟 AMD CPU 非常相似，甚至是九成九相同的「山寨」產品嗎？目前 Hygon 尚未公布 Dhyana CPU 的詳情，不過早一陣子有開發者將「 Hygon Dhyana Family 18h Processor 」加進 Linux Kernel 的支援時，其實過程也是將 AMD EPYC CPU（ Family 17h ） 的程式編碼，複製改成 Hygon Dhyana CPU 的 Linux Kernel 編碼，意味著 Hygon Dhyana CPU 和 AMD EPYC CPU 沒甚麼分別，只是品牌和型號名稱不同，兩者幾乎一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/add-dhyana-to-linux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fadd-dhyana-to-linux.png&h=928e0ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有程式員更新 Linux Kernel，以支援海光的 Dhyana x86 架構 CPU。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/same-linux-kernel-dhyana.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fsame-linux-kernel-dhyana.png&h=5705d1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">該程式員表示， Hygon Dhyana Family 18 處理器與 AMD EPYC 處理器架構十分相似。</span></div>"},{"pid":"cee6eb9767a55ae877c9b5d0a22d49d69230e677","tid":736271,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>AMD 與中國企業合資生產</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n兩個品牌的 CPU 一樣，又怎可能是合法設計生產？ x86 CPU 架構授權不是只有 Intel 、 AMD 和 VIA 擁有麼？ AMD 又為何容許如此相似的產品出現呢？當然 AMD 不是傻，故事就要說到 2016 年，當 AMD 的營運仍是岌岌可危，近乎走投無路的時候了。那時 AMD 就想到與中國的天津海光先進技術投資有限公司（ THATIC ）成立合資公司，一同發展 x86 架構處理器來「救亡」，而為了避免違反 AMD 與 Intel 於 2009 年簽署的交叉許可協議， AMD 與 THATIC 做了一連串事情來解決 x86 架構授權不可轉讓的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/amd-thatic-ownership-table.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Famd-thatic-ownership-table.png&h=7a483e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">AMD 與 THATIC 雙方於 HMC 和 Hygon 的股權比例。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n首先 AMD 與 THATIC 透過合資的形式成立了兩間新公司，一間是海光微電子技術有限公司（ HMC ），而另一間就是成都海光集成電路設計有限公司（ Hygon ，即上述 Dhyana CPU 所屬品牌）， AMD 與 THATIC 各佔的股權比例可見下表。據中國新浪網的報道，由於 x86 CPU 授權只可由 AMD 擁有，不得轉讓，因此 HMC 有 51% 股權屬於 AMD，而 HMC 就名正言順享有 x86 授權。然後 Hygon 就向 HMC 購買 x86 授權，來進行處理器的設計，再將設計好的處理器委託給 HMC 生產，那麼 HMC 便可以在合符規則的情況下，再找代工廠如台積電、 Samsung 等進行代工。完成好的產品就可以賣給 Hygon，以 Hygon 的名義於市場銷售。聽起來很複雜，不過 Hygon Dhyana 系列 CPU 就是經過兩間 AMD 與 THATIC 合資公司「左手交右手」共同研發，才得以合法推出市場。"},{"pid":"93a0f1a9e27dff98087ca81a5385bad455802f4a","tid":736271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>限於中國發售</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n一旦 Hygon Dhyana CPU 開始大量出貨，便是 AMD 的收成期，因為每顆售出的 Dhyana CPU ， AMD 都可以從中賺取 x86 架構授權的使用費，形成穩定收益，所以當 AMD 於 2016 年公布與 THATIC 合作時， AMD 的股價就隨即暴升 50%，另外亦會陸續收到 THATIC 的合共 2.93 億美元現金，成功挽救局勢。而現在外媒 Tom&rsquo;s Hardware 就透露 Hygon Dhyana CPU 已進入開始生產的階段（<a href=\"https://www.tomshardware.com/news/china-zen-x86-processor-dryhana,37417.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomshardware.com%2Fnews%2Fchina-zen-x86-processor-dryhana%2C37417.html&d=G3HZ6pmG21M7rxM7%2BVX0BXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2853bc77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tomshardware.com/news/china-zen-x86-processor-dryhana,37417.html</a>），雖然製成品只限於中國銷售，但由於中國數據中心、雲端及伺服器市場相當龐大，所以如此蹺蹊的策略，亦預期能助 AMD 於中國闖出一片天。"},{"pid":"4007739d77e351919b03e7adc91ca1347062a897","tid":736271,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">poweroff大佬你走先，我幫你頂住</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ede1d5b5e4a40c9b4017e3a8c32e2b5c294c3ee","tid":736271,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"點賣先？"},{"pid":"75957a303ffcfdea336e75377184b19f813d04bc","tid":736271,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ede1d5b5e4a40c9b4017e3a8c32e2b5c294c3ee","tid":736271,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"點賣先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又有興趣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"eda20c6293ecabdcb59850166fb58ca0322af854","tid":736271,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"會否加料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55783a04f17ed8d646af5c760a6d6787e64d32a4","tid":736271,"uid":28563