img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCore好似唔洗本咁有咁多堆咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"而家amd只授權中國用一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n二代另外買 同arm授權一樣 但amd x86 只能睇不能改"},{"pid":"f2bbc97dd34f261bc917822596a0b2b1df627389","tid":736271,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"中囯又成大贏家<br />\n第日冇中囯會唔會全世界都冇U用？"},{"pid":"55c095388e283b6a82f63b8e1a714e9501c25d0a","tid":736271,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"只怕契丹人又山塞咗當自己嘢！"}]}